-- GROUP BY suite, test



SELECT 
    push_timestamp as date,
    test,
    suite,
    platform,
    repository.name as repository,
    value
FROM performance_datum
    INNER JOIN performance_signature ON performance_datum.signature_id = performance_signature.id
    INNER JOIN machine_platform ON performance_signature.platform_id = machine_platform.id
    INNER JOIN repository ON performance_datum.repository_id = repository.id
    INNER JOIN job ON performance_datum.job_id = job.id
    INNER JOIN job_type on job.job_type_id = job_type.id
WHERE 
    push_timestamp > (CURRENT_DATE - INTERVAL '95' DAY)
    AND (repository.name = 'mozilla-central')
    AND suite LIKE '%browser_ml%'
